jobs.body_en:
Ad title:
Head of Marketing and Sales, Personal Assistant
Provided By:
Loft Towers
Published:
15 January
/
Deadline:
15 February
The development company
LOFT TOWERS
is announcing a vacancy for the position of:
1.
Head of Marketing and Sales
.
Location:
Batumi
Industry: Development / Construction Sector
Main Duties and Responsibilities:
** Developing and implementing marketing strategies;
** Managing, monitoring, and supporting a small marketing team;
** Close collaboration with sales, product development teams, and top management to understand business needs and develop marketing plans;
** Supervising the creation and distribution of marketing materials, including digital content, printed materials, presentations, and advertisements;
** Ensuring compliance with brand guidelines;
** Monitoring market trends, competitor activities, and customer insights;
** Managing the company`s online visibility and digital marketing channels (website, social media, email campaigns, paid advertising);
** Enhancing the company`s brand awareness and reputation.
** Providing consultation to clients regarding real estate purchases;
** Participating in the preparation of visual materials;
** Contacting potential buyers, providing feedback, and sharing information;
** Creating and continuously updating the company`s property database;
** Organizing meetings and site visits, presenting project information, and providing required documentation;
** Working on improving sales and building long-term customer relationships, offering new products and services;
** Managing documentation during sales (project-related and legal documents);
** Developing sales systems;
** Continuously improving the sales office;
** Attracting partner companies ;
** Working with brokers, attracting new brokers, and signing agreements with existing ones;
** Developing, planning, and implementing sales strategies;
** Collecting client-related materials from architects, accountants, lawyers, and project managers;
** Managing the CRM system;
** Calculating and planning promotions/offers.
Qualification Requirements:
** Education: Bachelor`s degree in Marketing, Business Administration, or a related field; a Master`s degree is an advantage;
** Work Experience: At least 5 years of experience in marketing within the development sector, including 2 years in a managerial role;
** Languages: Fluent Georgian; English at minimum C1-Advanced level; Russian at B2-Upper-Intermediate level;
** Technical Knowledge & Skills: Experience in developing and executing successful marketing strategies (preferably in the banking/financial industry); strong knowledge of digital marketing tools and platforms, including website CMS, email marketing software, social media management tools, and analytics platforms; understanding of regulatory requirements and compliance standards related to marketing in the construction industry.
Skills:
** Presentable appearance;
** Strong communication skills;
** Proactiveness;
** Ability to work in a team;
** High sense of responsibility toward work;
** Effective communication, negotiation, and time-management skills.
Working Conditions:
** 5 working days / 2 days off;
** Work hours: 10:00-19:00;
** Workplace: Batumi, 31 Shota Rustaveli Street
Application Submission:
Please send your resume to the following email address:
Kobuleti2towers@gmail.com
Loft Towers wishes you success!
2.
Personal Assistant to the Director
We are looking for a highly organized, responsible, and detail-oriented Personal Assistant to the Director to support executive and operational activities within a real estate development company.
Key Responsibilities:
** Managing the Director`s daily schedule, calendar, and appointments
** Organizing and coordinating internal and external meetings (online/offline)
** Arranging business trips, site visits, and travel logistics
** Handling phone calls, emails, and official correspondence
** Preparing official letters, contracts, and internal documents
** Communicating with partners, investors, contractors, and stakeholders on behalf of the Director
** Providing Georgian/English translations when required
** Ensuring confidentiality of sensitive and corporate information
** Monitoring ongoing construction and investment projects
** Tracking deadlines and coordinating with responsible teams
** Communicating with architects, engineers, brokers, and government authorities
** Preparing meeting minutes and following up on action items
** Preparing reports, presentations, and briefings
** Supporting internal office processes and team coordination
** Handling ad hoc tasks and urgent requests
Qualifications:
** Higher education (preferred)
** Minimum 1 year of experience in a similar position
** Excellent command of Georgian and English (written and spoken)
** Strong organizational and time-management skills
** Ability to multitask and work under pressure
** High level of responsibility and attention to detail
** Proficiency in MS Office
** Experience in real estate or development field will be considered an advantage
Location:
Batumi, Rustaveli Street 31
How to Apply:
Interested candidates are kindly requested to send their CV to the following email address:
kobuleti2towers@gmail.com

